title: A unique film
review:
This has the potential to be a cult classic.

The acting is not great and the story not great but the unique style of the film and mannerisms keep you watching.

Give it a try.. you will either love it or hate it, but it is def a different type of film.

6.1

title: College
review: This is college. That's all you need to know. It's a running allegorical joke that only the guys who went to whatever college this is based on are in on. The saving grace is the delightfully maniacal performance by Logan Huffman as the head of the red fraternity, whose name escapes me. We all know a guy like that.
